    <h2>CHAPTER 5: TESTING AND RESULTS</h2>
    
    <h3>5.1 Testing Strategy</h3>
    <p>A V-Model strategy was used covering Unit Testing (GPA Logic), Integration Testing (Auth Flow via Postman), and System Testing (Apache Benchmark for load).</p>

    <h3>5.2 User Acceptance Testing (UAT)</h3>
    <p>Pilot users rated Ease of Use at 4.8/5.0. Key feedback highlighted the value of instant notifications for rejected documents.</p>

    <h3>5.3 Results Discussion</h3>
    <p>Turnaround time dropped from 14 days to 3 days. Arithmetic errors in GPA calculation were eliminated.</p>
